#

Zucchini Pizza Bites

25 min
$8
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetarianlow-carb

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

SnackAppetizer

Tags:

easyquickhealthysnack

Description

Delicious bite-sized pizzas made with zucchini instead of dough, topped with marinara sauce, cheese, and your favorite toppings!

Ingredients

  • zucchini: 2 medium
  • marinara sauce: 1 cup
  • shredded mozzarella cheese: 1 cup
  • pepperoni slices: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
